The paper presents a method for reinforcement learning using a model-based approach with model predictive control. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on real-time control of robotic systems, which further supports these categories.
